parameters: I was just wondering what could've happened
to you, but it's great that you're okay.
Sorry, I just couldn't keep my excitement
down, so I went ahead of you all.
How did you come here, Luora?
Aah, so Muracca did think of that.
To be honest, I'm stuck, too...
What do you mean by that?
Remember the door that you couldn't open
when you came out from the tunnel?
But I couldn't open it up, so I changed
directions and just jumped down the cliff.
We didn't account for such a method.
I figured it out ages ago,
you two were just overthinking too much.
Well, we've seen a fair bit, so...
Well, let's leave it at that.
Now that we don't have to worry about
this anymore, I feel much more at ease now──
So this is Ront, hm? Just as I've heard.
Muracca, the hunters are asking for you.
They'd like you to take care of it.
We'll accompany you, if you'd like.
Monsters escape from Lavigny all the time.
Just hit them and they run away like flies.
with your trip a fair bit.
It's a bit of a shame, Muracca.
I'd have loved to journey with you.
I'm sure such an opportunity will come someday.
It just wasn't the case this time.
Thanks for telling me this, Valco.
Now then, I shall depart myself.
...I was thinking of inviting Valco, too.
Well, can't be helped, I guess.
Just like Muracca said, some day
Alright, let us continue our adventure!
You'll be fighting with us, right?
ones fighting, are you kidding me?
I'm cheering you from the back!
I see, so fighting really does...
It's not about something that terrible...
I just wanted to be protected by Ino
on a whim, is that so bad?
Why are you pumped all of a sudden?
\C[17]The New Ancient Forest\C[0]'s details have been updated.
What kind of place is this?
I heard from Muracca that Miss Tahati
has expressed concern about this location.
Perhaps it's more than a simple forest?
It never really felt like a forest,
but more like a ruins site.
I don't know about that either──
Well, isn't understanding the world around you
the whole point of an adventure?
I seem to have gone off-topic, sorry.
Isn't walking around without a goal,
If we're talking goals, I've got one.
About the story of the departure from Tantali.
I know it existed, I suppose.
It's how we met \N[11], after all.
I see. Then I should tell you that
this forest likely that departure's purpose.
I feel we'll get along just fine!
Adventuring's more fun if you have a clear goal.
We might find some treasure here?
There's something with that name here.
Will woof's travel end if we find
If you're fine with that, then
I guess that's it, young one.
Well, that's not a bad goal.
But even if the scope is limited to this forest,
the exact location is still rather vague.
It's said to be "located in the southern end".
...But it'll definitely be a difficult venture.
If only there's a place we can use as a base around...
